msgid "To install using pip::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro/install.rst:27
msgid "pip install Scrapy"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro/install.rst:29
msgid "To install using easy_install::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro/install.rst:31
msgid "easy_install Scrapy"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro/install.rst:36
msgid "Platform specific installation notes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro/install.rst:39
msgid "Windows"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro/install.rst:41
msgid "After installing Python, follow these steps before installing Scrapy:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro/install.rst:43
msgid ""
"add the ``C:\\python27\\Scripts`` and ``C:\\python27`` folders to the system "
"path by adding those directories to the ``PATH`` environment variable from "
"the `Control Panel`_."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro/install.rst:47
msgid "install OpenSSL by following these steps:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro/install.rst:49
msgid ""
"go to `Win32 OpenSSL page <http://slproweb.com/products/Win32OpenSSL.html>`_"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro/install.rst:51
msgid ""
"download Visual C++ 2008 redistributables for your Windows and architecture"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro/install.rst:53
msgid ""
"download OpenSSL for your Windows and architecture (the regular version, not "
"the light one)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro/install.rst:55
msgid ""
"add the ``c:\\openssl-win32\\bin`` (or similar) directory to your ``PATH``, "
"the same way you added ``python27`` in the first step`` in the first step"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro/install.rst:57
msgid ""
"some binary packages that Scrapy depends on (like Twisted, lxml and "
"pyOpenSSL) require a compiler available to install, and fail if you don't "
"have Visual Studio installed. You can find Windows installers for those in "
"the following links. Make sure you respect your Python version and Windows "
"architecture."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro/install.rst:59
msgid "pywin32: http://sourceforge.net/projects/pywin32/files/"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro/install.rst:60
msgid "Twisted: http://twistedmatrix.com/trac/wiki/Downloads"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro/install.rst:61
msgid ""
"zope.interface: download the egg from `zope.interface pypi page <http://pypi."
"python.org/pypi/zope.interface>`_ and install it by running ``easy_install "
"file.egg``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro/install.rst:62
msgid "lxml: http://pypi.python.org/pypi/lxml/"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../intro/install.rst:63
msgid "pyOpenSSL: https://launchpad.net/pyopenssl"
msgstr ""

